\id 2PE
\h 2 Pita
\toc1 Leta Theghewoniye Pita Le Rorori
\toc2 2 Pita
\toc3 2Pit
\mt2 Leta Theghewoniye
\mt1 Pita
\mt2 Le Rorori
\imt1 Utu iviva
\ip Pita le mare vama i gheneghenetha ambama i roriva letake iyake na i variye weŇčgiya raloŇčweloŇčweghath…® thiya yaku e val…®vaŇčga na val…®vaŇčga (1:1 na 3:1). Ravavaghare kwan…®kwan lemoyo th…® wovathovuthovuyeŇča thanavu raithar…® na th…® utu kwan th…®Ňčava Jisas mane i njoghama. Iya kaiwae Pita i vavur…®ghegheŇčgiya raloŇčweloŇčweghath…® na thava th…® goru weya vavaghare kwan…®kwan…®ko iyako.
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Ghino Saimon Pita, Jisas Krais le rakakaiwo na ghal…®Ňčae gharaghamb…®. Ya roriya letake iyake na i ghaona e ghemi, thavala kaero hu loŇčweghath…® Ňčgoreiya ghime. Ra wo loŇčweghath…®ke iyake weya Jisas Krais, iye la Loi na la Ravamoru, le thovuye e t…®ne e la loŇčweghath…®, na loŇčweghath…®ko iyako gham…®nae i thovuye moli weinda.
\v 2 Ya naŇčgo na mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye Loi i mwaewo weŇčga na le gharemal…®l…® i riyevanjara gharemina kaiwae Loi na ghanda Giya Jisas ghanjighareghare kaero ina e ghemi.
\s1 Loi le kula na le tuthi
\p 
\v 3 Loi le vur…®gheghe e t…®ne, Krais kaerova i giya weinda bigibigike wolagh…®ye nuwandaiya na val…®kaiwanda ra yaku Ňčgoreiya Loi yawaliye na i boboma. Bigibigike wolagh…®ye thiyake ghinda kaiwanda, kaiwae ra ghareghare wagiyaweya Krais. I kula weinda na ra wo weinda le vwenyevwenyeko na le thovuyeko.
\v 4 Thiyake kaiwanji kaerova i giya weinda, giya bwagabwaga lagh…®lagh…®ye na thovuthovuye va i dagerawe, na thiyake kaiwanji mbala hu voiteta yawal…® raraithar…® th…® yoyomara ghar…®ghar…® e lenji renuwaŇča t…®ne e yambaneke, na mbala ghinda Loi le ŇčgamaŇčgama na Ňčgoreinda amalagh…®niye.
\v 5 Kaiwae Krais kaerova i vakatha bigibigike wolagh…®ye thiyake, hu rovur…®gheghe hu vatabo thanavu thovuye e lemi loŇčweghath…®na e vwatae; na e ghemi thanavuna thovuye hu vatabo Loi e ghaghareghare;
\v 6 na Loi e ghaghareghare hu vatabo tembe ghamimberegha e ghaminjimbukiki; e ghaminjimbukiki hu vatabo e ghataŇčaghath…®; na e ghataŇčaghath…® hu vatabo e Kristiyan yawaliye;
\v 7 na e Kristiyan yawaliye hu vatabo e gharemwaewo; na e gharemwaewo hu vavatabo e gharethovu.
\v 8 ThoŇčgo thanavu thovuye kamwath…®niyeke thiyake ina e yawalimina na mbe th…® mbuthumbuthu vara, ne th…® vakatha lemi renuwaŇča i voru weiye lemi vakatha thovuye, na ghanda Giya Jisas Krais ghaghareghare mbe i lagh…®lagh…®ye vara e ghemi.
\v 9 Thela raloŇčweloŇčweghath…® na thanavuke thiyake ma ina e yawaliye, iye lolo marae i kwaghe o lolo ma i thuwe na thovuye kaiwae kaero i renuwaŇča vaghalawe le thar…® va i vakathaŇčgi, na Loi kaero i numoten…®Ňčgi.
\p 
\v 10 Iya kaiwae, lo bodaboda, hu rovur…®gheghe lagh…®ye na hu vakatha Loi le kula na le tututhina e ghemi i emunjoru e yawalimina. ThoŇčgo hu vakatha Ňčgoreiya ko mane mbaŇča regha hu dobu e lemi loŇčweghath…®na.
\v 11 Iyake kaiwae Loi ne i vatomwe emunjoru moli e ghemi weiye ghanda Giya Jisas Krais lenji ghamba mbaro na vohu ruwe.
\p 
\v 12 Iya kaiwae mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye ne ya vanuwov…®r…®Ňčga bigibigike thiyake kaiwanji, othembe kaero hu ghareghare na hu vatad…®Ňčga e emunjoruko iya kaerova th…® vaghareŇčgana.
\v 13 Ya renuwaŇča mbema i thovuye eŇčge vara moli e ghino na ya th…®n…®vavair…®Ňčga e lemi renuwaŇčakiki bigibigike thiyake kaiwanji Ňčgora vara amba e yawayawaliŇčguke.
\v 14 Ya ghareghare mbaŇča ubotu ya roiteta yawal…®ke iyake, Ňčgoreiya ghanda Giya Jisas Krais le govambwara e ghino.
\v 15 Ne ya mando na ya rovur…®gheghe na ya vivatharaweya kamwath…® regha ghemi kaiwami, mbala i vakathaŇčga na hu renuwaŇčakikiŇčgiya bigibigike thiyake mbaŇča ghino kaero nandere.
\s1 Krais le vwenyevwenye gharathuweŇčgi
\p 
\v 16 Ma wo ndeghath…® e riuriu ma e r…®gher…®ghenji na wo utuŇča e ghemi ghanda Giya Jisas Krais le njoghama na ne le vur…®gheghe. Mbe e marame vara wo thuweya le vwenyevwenye.
\v 17 Kaiwae va iname gheko mbaŇča Loi Ramae i giya ghayavwatata na i wovavwenyevwenyeŇča, na e mbaŇčako iyako ghal…®ghal…®Ňča regha i menawe ele ghamba vwenyevwenyeko t…®ne, iŇča, ‚ÄúIyake naruŇčgu val…®ghareghareŇčgu, i vakathaŇčgo ya warari lagh…®ye moli.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 1:17 \xt Mat 17:5; Mak 9:7; Luk 9:35\x*
\v 18 Mbe ghime vara wo loŇčweya ghal…®ghal…®Ňčako iyako i njama e buruburu, mbaŇča va weime e ouko boboma vwatae.
\p 
\v 19 Iya kaiwae weime lama vareminje emunjoru totoko iya ghal…®Ňčae gharautu va th…® utuŇčako. Ne i thalavuŇčga thoŇčgo hu ndeghath…®we, kaiwae iye Ňčgoreiya theŇčgi i woya e momouwo gheghada igh…®viya rakaraka na th…®nambaŇčako manjamanjalawae i vakake gharemina.
\v 20 Ko iyemaeŇčge iviva moli wo hu ghareghareya iyake; ma lolo regha mbe ghambereghaeŇčge val…®kaiwae i vamanjamanjalaŇča ghal…®Ňčae gharautu lenji utu Buk Boboma e t…®ne.
\v 21 Kaiwae ma ghal…®Ňčae gharautu regha va ghamberegha le renuwaŇča e t…®ne na i utuŇča, ko iyemaeŇčge ghal…®Ňčae gharautu Nyao Boboma va i vambaroŇčaŇčgi na th…® utuŇča toto i mena weya Loi.
\c 2
\s1 Ravavaghare kwan…®kwan…®Ňčgi
\p 
\v 1 Ghal…®Ňčae gharautu kwan…®kwan…®Ňčgi va th…® yomara weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® me vivako, na ravavaghare kwan…®kwan…®Ňčgi tembe ne th…® yomarava e ghemi. Thiye ne th…® womena vavaghare Ňčgoreiya vathevather…® na ma emunjoru, na th…® wovakwan…®kwan…®Ňča Giya iye va i vamodoŇčgi, iya kaiwae tembene th…® womenava ghanjimberegha weŇčgi vuyowo lagh…®ye moli.
\v 2 Othembe iyako, ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo ne th…® ghambugha ghanjithanavuko raithar…®ko, na lenji vakathako kaiwae vavana ne th…® wovathar…®thar…®Ňča emunjoru kamwath…®niye.
\v 3 E lenji vothako t…®ne, ravavaghare kwan…®kwan…®Ňčgike thiyake e lenji utu kwan…®kwan…®ko th…® vaidiya ghathovuye. MbaŇča va i vivako Loi kaerova i vakatha ghanjimbaro na ne i giya vuyowo weŇčgi, kaiwae iye ma i ghena na ne i vakatha Ňčgoreiye va iŇča ne i vakatha weŇčgi.
\p 
\v 4 Loi va i giya vuyowo weŇčgiya nyao va th…® vakatha thar…®, na i bigiraweŇčgi e momouwo t…®ne thambe, na gheko th…® roroghagha ghaghad mbaŇčaniye Loi ghambaŇča Mbaro.
\v 5 Ra ghareghare Loi va i vakatha vuyowo weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® me vivako, na i vakatha thotho na i gaboŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® ma th…® ghambugha amalagh…®niye. Ghar…®ghar…® va i vamoruŇčgi, Nowa, iye thanavu thovuye gharautu na ghaune theghepir…®.
\v 6 Loi va i guraŇčgiya ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye ghembaiwo ‚ÄĒ Sodoma na Gomora na i mukuwoŇčgi e nd…®ghe. Va i vakatha iyako na thiye Ňčgoreiya ghamba thuwathuwa weŇčgiya thavala ma th…® ghambugha Loi ghathanavu.
\v 7 Ko iyemaeŇčge va i thalavugha Lote, iye lolo thovuye, na amalagh…®niye mava i warari Sodoma ghar…®ghar…®niye ghanjithanavu kaiwae,
\v 8 kaiwae iye lolo thovuye, na mbaŇča regha na regha i ghataŇča v…®r…® lagh…®ye ghauneko e t…®nenji, i thuwe na i loŇčweya lenji vakathako raraithar…® kaiwae.
\v 9 Na thoŇčgo Ňčgoreiyako, Giya i ghareghare ŇčgoroŇčga ne iŇča na i thalavuŇčgiya thavala th…® ghambugha ghathanavu e ghanjimando t…®ne, na ŇčgoroŇčga na ne i giya vuyowo weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® raraithar…® gheghad ne ghambaŇča Mbaro,
\v 10 thiye Ňčgoranjiya thavala th…® ghambugha riwanjiko le renuwaŇča na th…® wovathar…®thar…®Ňča Loi le mbaro.
\p Ravavaghare kwan…®kwan…®Ňčgike thiyake th…® vata e lenji ghareghare e vwatae na i wovoreŇčaŇčgi na ma e lenji yavwatata weŇčgiya buruburu vur…®ghegheniyeŇčgi, iyemaeŇčge th…® utuvathar…® weŇčgi.
\v 11 Othembe nyao thovuthovuye ‚ÄĒ thiye th…® lagh…®ye na th…® vur…®gheghe kivwalaŇčgiya ravavaghare kwan…®kwan…®Ňčgi ‚ÄĒ ma th…® guraŇčgiya buruburu vur…®ghegheniye e utuutu raraithar…® Giya e marae.
\v 12 Ko iyemaeŇčge ghar…®ghar…®ke thiyake lenji vakatha ma weiye lenji renuwaŇča thovuye, Ňčgoranjiya thetheghan mbwanjam th…® ghamb…® gabo kaiwae. Thiye th…® utuvathar…® weya the bigi ma th…® gharegharena thovuye kaiwae. Nevole th…® mukuwoŇčgi Ňčgoreiya thetheghan mbwanjam,
\v 13 na kaiwae th…® vakatha ghar…®ghar…® vavana th…® vaidiva vuyowo, thiye tembene th…® vaidiva vuyowae. Th…® renuwaŇča lenji ghamba warari th…® ghan…®Ňčga na th…® munumu i ghanagha othembe ghararagh…®ye, i vakavakathaŇčgi nuwanji i loghe mbaŇča th…® ru e ghemi na th…® ghan…®Ňčga. Iyake kaiwae th…® vakowana idaidami thovuthovuye na th…® vamonjinaŇčaŇčga.
\v 14 Maranjiko mbe i loghelogheŇčaŇčgi vara wanakau; thar…® ghavakatha e gham…®nanjiko ma mbaŇča regha kaero i vamboromboro. Th…® yaroŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® lenji loŇčweghath…® ma i vur…®gheghe na th…® wona. Th…® vavaghare yawalinji e kurakura thanavuniye na Loi nevole i giya vuyowo weŇčgi.
\v 15 Kaero th…® roiteta yawal…® thovuye na th…® vur…®thavwiya ghakamwath…®, na kaero th…® vur…®mban Balaam Beo nariye ele kamwath…®, iye ghare weya mani i mban…®mba na i vakavakatha thar…®.
\v 16 Ko iyemaeŇčge le doŇč…®ki va i ravaghawe e thanavuko iyako. Thetheghan…®ko va i utu Ňčgoreiya lolo na i vanamwe e ghathar…®ko kaiwae.
\p 
\v 17 Ghar…®ghar…®ke thiyake Ňčgoranjiya mborowou kaero th…®ma, na Ňčgoranjiya Ňčgal…®l…® ndewendewe vur…®gheghe i tagavewoŇčgi. Loi kaerova i vivatharaweya ghambanji, e momouwo t…®ne.
\v 18 MbaŇča th…® vavaghare weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®, budakaiya lenji renuwaŇčako th…®Ňčava iye bigi lagh…®ye ko iyemaeŇčge ma e uneune; na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, th…® utuŇča weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko val…®kaiwanji eŇčge th…® vakatha the vakatha iya riwanjiko nuwaiya na th…® vakatha. Rakwan…®ko th…® wo lenji utuutuko thiyako na th…® valogha ghar…®ghar…®ko nuwanji na th…® roiteta emunjoruko yakuyakuniye. Ghar…®ghar…®ko thiyako vamba th…® viyathu eŇčge iya thanavuko raraithar…® ghanjivakatha.
\v 19 Ravavaghare kwan…®kwan th…® dagerawe weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® na th…®Ňčava thiye kaero rakarakayathuŇčgi, ko thiye ghanjimberegha thar…® i mbaroŇčaŇčgi ‚ÄĒ kaiwae the bigithan kaero i kivwala na i laweghath…®gha loloko iyako kaero i kivwala iyena.
\v 20 Kaiwae thoŇčgo ghar…®ghar…® kaerova th…® roiteta thar…®ko wolagh…®ye yawaliye e yambaneke, th…® ghareghareya ghanda Giya na ghanda Ravamoru Jisas Krais, na i njana thanavuko iyako mbowo i laweghath…®Ňčgiva, ghar…®ghar…®ko thiyako kaero inanji e vuyowo lagh…®ye moli t…®ne; i kivwala va i vivako.
\v 21 Ghar…®ghar…®ko thiyako mbalava i thovuye moli weŇčgi thoŇčgo ma mbaŇča regha th…® ghareghareya thanavu thovuye ghakamwath…®, iya i vatomweya yawal…®ko Loi nuwaiya ghar…®ghar…® th…® yakuŇča. Ko mbaŇča th…® roiteta totoko thovuye iya kaerova th…® woko, thiye kaero inanji e vuyowo lagh…®ye moli t…®ne, i kivwala va i vivako.
\v 22 Budakai i yomara weŇčgi i woraŇčgiya goghaimbaŇčgike thiyake emunjoru: ‚ÄúMbugha tembe i ghan…®va budakaiya me thegharaŇčgiya‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 2:22 \xt Vav 26:11\x* na ‚ÄúMbombo kaero me thithu i njogha na tembe ve wowagh…®va.‚ÄĚ
\c 3
\s1 Giya le njoghama utuniye
\p 
\v 1 Ae wouna na val…®ghareghareŇčgu, iyake lo leta yaŇčgaiwoniye ya rori na ya variye e ghemi. E letaŇčgike yaŇčgaiwoke iyake e t…®nenji ya mando na ya vaira renuwaŇča emunjoru e yawalimina iya kaiwae ya vanuwov…®r…®Ňčga bigibigike thiyake kaiwanji.
\v 2 NuwaŇčguiya hu renuwaŇčakikiŇčgiya utuutu ghal…®Ňčae gharautu va th…® utuŇča mbaŇča me vivako. Na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva ghanda Giya na Ravamoru le vavaghare, iyava ghal…®Ňčae gharaghamb…® th…® vaghareŇčgana.
\v 3 I viva moli val…®kaiwami hu ghareghareya iyake: mbaŇča le ghambako kaero i gheneghenetha na ghar…®ghar…® vavana ne th…® yoyomara, thanavu raraithar…® i mbaroŇčaŇčgiya yawalinjiko. Ne th…® vav…®r…®Ňčga
\v 4 na ne th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúVa i dagerawe na iŇča ne i njoghama, ae? Ko aŇčgama inae? Orumburumbunda kaerova thiya mare, ko iyemaeŇčge bigibigike wolagh…®ye mbe Ňčgoreiye vara va i rikowe gheghada noroke.‚ÄĚ
\v 5 Emunjoru th…® renuwaŇča vaghalawa iya emunjoruke iyake: mbaŇča va i vivako Loi e ghal…®Ňčae buruburu i yomara, na yambaneke i yomara i raŇčgima e mbwa t…®ne.
\v 6 Na te vambe mbwava, mbwa va i thotho na i mukuwa yambaneke.
\v 7 Ko buruburu na yambaneke mbaŇčake e ghal…®Ňčae na tene i mukuwoŇčgi e nd…®ghe. Mbene th…® yakuyaku vara ghaghad mbaŇčaniye vara ghar…®ghar…® ma th…® ghambugha Loi ne i woraweya ghanjimbaro na i mukuwoŇčgi.
\p 
\v 8 Ko iyemaeŇčge, ae wouna na val…®ghareghareŇčgu, thava hu renuwaŇča vaghalawa emunjoruke iyake! Giya ma i rughiya mbaŇča le molamolao Ňčgoreiye ghinda. Amalagh…®niyewe mbaŇča regha na theghathegha hoserithaŇčar…® ghanjilughawoghawo ma i tomethi. Ghinda ra renuwaŇča mbaŇčake noroke ghalughawoghawo ubotu na theghathegha hoserithaŇčar…® ghalughawoghawo molao moli, ko amalagh…®niyewe th…® mboromboro.
\v 9 Giya iyewe ma i vuyowo budakai i dagerawe ne i vakatha, Ňčgoreiye vavana th…®Ňča le njoghama i vuyowo. IyemaeŇčge weiye le riwouda e ghemi kaiwae ma nuwaiya thar…®, ko iyemaeŇčge nuwaiya taulagh…®ke ghinda ra roiteta ghandathanavu raraithar…®.
\p 
\v 10 Ko Giya ghambaŇča ne i mena Ňčgoreiya rakaiv…® le vutha. Ne e MbaŇčako iyako buruburu i ghawe na labut…®ye lagh…®ye, buruburu matemate ne thiya nda na i mukuwoŇčgi, na yambaneke weiye bigibiginiyeke wolagh…®ye ne th…® ghawe moli.
\p 
\v 11 MbaŇča bigibigike wolagh…®ye thiyake ne i mukuwoŇčgi e kamwath…®ke iyake, iya kaiwae ghemi mbala hu boboma na yawalimina lagh…®ye hu vatomwe weya Loi.
\v 12 MbaŇča hu roroghagha Loi ne ghambaŇča mbaro na hu rovur…®gheghe kaiwae na mbala le mena i maya ‚ÄĒ ne e mbaŇčaniye buruburu ne i yolamwe na i mukuwo, na buruburu matemate ne th…® woivao dayaghako kaiwae.
\v 13 Ko kaiwae kaerova i dagerawe, ra roroghagha buruburu togha na yambane togha ne Ňčgoreiya thanavu thovuye ghembaniye.
\p 
\v 14 Iya kaiwae wouna na val…®ghareghareŇčgu, e lemi roroghagha mbaŇčako iyako kaiwae, hu rovur…®gheghe na hu kakaleva na thava e lemi thar…® nasiye Loi e marae namoghamwami weimi.
\v 15 Giya iye rariwouda na le riwoudako iyako e t…®ne i giya ghar…®ghar…® ghanjimbaŇča na th…® vaidiya ghanjivamoru, Ňčgoreiya ghaghanda Pol va i rorori e ghemi. Va i vakaiwoŇča thimbako iyava Loi i giyakowe.
\v 16 E le letako wolagh…®ye e t…®nenji bigibigi vavana i utuŇča utuninji th…® vuyowo na thavala ma e lenji ghareghare na ma lenji loŇčweghath…® i lagh…®ye th…® vamanjamanjalaŇča vathar…®. Tembe th…® vakathava Ňčgoreiye e utuutu vavanava Buk Boboma e t…®ne. Tembe thiye ghanjimberegha th…® womena vuyowo weŇčgi ne mbaŇča ele ghambako.
\p 
\v 17 Iya kaiwae, wouna na val…®ghareghareŇčgu, kaero hu ghareghareya iyake. Tembe ghamimberegha hu njimbukikiŇčga mbala ma val…®kaiwae ghar…®ghar…® raraithar…® th…® vaŇčguŇčga na vohu ru kwan ele val…®vaŇčga na hu dobu e lemi ghamba ndeghath…® thovuye.
\v 18 Ko iyemaeŇčge hu rombele na mbe hu mbuthumbuthu vara ghanda Giya na Ravamoru Jisas Krais le mwaewo bwagabwaga e t…®ne na hu ghareghare wagiyaweya amalagh…®niye. Tarawa na yavwatata i voro weya amalagh…®niye noroke na mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye. Mbwana, Ňčgoreiye. 
